{"tid":348677,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本人正式發起舉報乞衣活動!","createTime":"2017-08-06T02:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T05:13:43.000Z","uid":115316,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"715639b15224298c8cbbe17c6ac7ded8c0baa6e0","tid":348677,"uid":115316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T02:31:54.000Z","msg":"幾日前行過中環 一條天橋幾檔乞兒<br />\n啲鬼佬喺度乞錢俾佢旅行 假到仆街<br />\n<br />\n為阻止行乞呃錢風氣喺香港蔓延<br />\n希望各位連登仔一齊參加<br />\n見一個乞衣舉報一個<br />\n順便又可以幫班警察創造工作機會<br />\n<br />\n根據香港法例 ，任何人在任何公眾地方乞取或收取施捨，均有可能觸犯香港法例第228章《簡易程序治罪條例》第26A條。如屬第一或第二次定罪，可處罰款500元及監禁一個月；如屬第三次或其後定罪，可處罰款500元及監禁十二個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e369ee385fb39078a982b1cf6cb61538e1a6eb","tid":348677,"uid":115316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T02:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5539d3da798d6ed0f88ef7776840aa8da740880c","tid":348677,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T02:45:54.000Z","msg":"順便搞埋假和尚,支那狗唱歌籌錢,收cd收酒"},{"pid":"15ac596f6e42c3129afcc9109215618beed92b7e","tid":348677,"uid":115316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T02:57:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>順便搞埋假和尚,支那狗唱歌籌錢,收cd收酒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n假和尚行乞都係犯同一條罪<br />\n<br />\n其他唔清楚有冇犯法<br />\n有請法律撚"},{"pid":"ad192eaca2043181c2702a3395b17f8104baba0a","tid":348677,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T02:57:43.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n個埋鬼佬賣左成兩年都仲係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1efb0a84a6fe2e632453200e676496856c76f23b","tid":348677,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T02:58:18.000Z","msg":"要啦"},{"